<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Planna – Plan Your Perfect Event</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/layout.css" />
</head>

<body>
  <%- include("./partials/_logo") %>
  <div class="layout-home">
    <main class="content">

      <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-overlay">
          <div class="hero-content centered">
            <h1 class="heading">Say "I Do" to planning like a Pro!</h1>
            <p class="intro-text">Effortlessly plan weddings, parties, and events with all your vendors, guests, RSVPs,
              and tasks in one place.</p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
              <a href="/auth/sign-up" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
              <a href="/auth/sign-in" class="btn btn-secondary">Already have an account?</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="how-it-works" class="section how-it-works">
        <h2 class="subheading">How It Works</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">
          Planna makes event planning intuitive and stress-free. Create an event, link your vendors, track budgets, and
          manage tasks and RSVPs—all in one place.
        </p>

        <div class="how-it-works-grid">
          <div class="how-step">
            <h3>1. Create an Event</h3>
            <p>Start by entering your event’s name, date, and location.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="how-step">
            <h3>2. Add Vendors & Guests</h3>
            <p>Invite guests, assign vendors, and keep everything organized.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="how-step">
            <h3>3. Track Everything</h3>
            <p>Stay on top of RSVPs, tasks, budgets, and vendor payments.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="how-step">
            <h3>4. Celebrate Stress-Free</h3>
            <p>Enjoy your event knowing Planna took care of the chaos.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <img src="/img/dashboard.jpg" alt="Planna Dashboard Screenshot" class="section-image" />
        <div class="cta-wrapper">
          <a href="/auth/sign-up" class="btn btn-primary">Set Up Dashboard</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section stats">
        <h2 class="subheading">Our Impact</h2>
        <div class="stats-grid">
          <div class="stat-box">
            <h3>5,000+</h3>
            <p>Events Successfully Planned</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-box">
            <h3>3,800+</h3>
            <p>Happy Customers</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-box">
            <h3>12,000+</h3>
            <p>Active Users</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section testimonials">
        <h2 class="subheading">What Our Users Say</h2>
        <div class="testimonials-grid">
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <p>“Planna made our wedding planning so easy! We loved tracking everything in one place.”</p>
            <strong>– Sarah & Mike</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <p>“I hosted a corporate retreat and Planna kept me on schedule and on budget.”</p>
            <strong>– Jason A.</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <p>“Vendors loved it, I loved it, and my birthday was amazing thanks to this app.”</p>
            <strong>– Elina R.</strong>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="footer-content">
        <div class="footer-left">
          <h3>Planna</h3>
          <p>Making event planning delightful and stress-free.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-center">
          <p><strong>Contact Us:</strong></p>
          <p>Email: support@planna.com</p>
          <p>Phone: (555) 123-4567</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-right">
          <p><strong>Follow Us</strong></p>
          <a href="#" class="social-link">Instagram</a>
          <a href="#" class="social-link">Facebook</a>
          <a href="#" class="social-link">Twitter</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Planna. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>

</html>